396f5c537d776c251d45fe435188ccd68a856749.query: SELECT subscription_id FROM subscriptions WHERE kind = 'discord_stream_update' AND (payload ->> 'channel_id') = $1 AND (payload ->> 'guild_id') = $2 AND (payload ->> 'vtuber_id') = $3

3e2c42646bfc82c0ab3033100569ee0ed5d01461.query:
INSERT INTO stream_viewer_stats AS s (stream_id, time, count)
     VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
ON CONFLICT (stream_id, time) DO UPDATE
        SET count = GREATEST(excluded.count, s.count)

725e5036f434538e9413a7aad06ae6601ec557fb.query:
UPDATE streams
        SET viewer_max = GREATEST(viewer_max, $1),
            viewer_avg = (SELECT AVG(count) FROM stream_viewer_stats WHERE stream_id = $2),
            updated_at = $3
      WHERE stream_id = $2

74bab5728e6602040e7d103ed51f0da94315a0bd.query:
INSERT INTO vtubers (vtuber_id, native_name, english_name, japanese_name, twitter_username, thumbnail_url)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)

a776980e570e14df4951d06bb67971cda0110912.query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM vtubers WHERE vtuber_id = $1

ad7b071f04921216253c2c5e41a6fabf96a654df.query: UPDATE jobs SET status = 'queued', last_run = NOW(), updated_at = NOW() WHERE job_id = $1

faa15d2c0d8e70002982fe6383c133fca6e6b90c.query: UPDATE notifications SET updated_at = NOW() WHERE notification_id = $1
